Introduction

XLOV is a 4-member South Korean multinational boy group under 257 Entertainment (formerly known as JPark & Company). The group consists of Wumuti, Rui, Haru, and Hyun. They debuted on January 7, 2025, with their first single album "I’mma Be."

On December 17th Wumuti, a former Boys Planet contestant and member of the group WaterFire was announced as the first member. On the 19th former Boys Planet contestant Rui was announced as the second member, later on the 21st member Hyun was revealed, on the 23rd, former Boys Planet contestant Haru was revealed as the final member.

On January 14, 2025, they announced that their official fandom name will be EVOL, which is a reverse of the word 'Love'
